Package: ggdark
Type: Package
Title: Dark Mode for ggplot2 Themes
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Neal Grantham
Maintainer: Neal Grantham <neal@nsgrantham.com>
Description: Activate dark mode on your favorite ggplot2 theme 
             with ggdark::darken. The black, white, and 
             greyscale theme elements are inverted, and geom 
             defaults of fill and color are changed to white.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 3.1)
Imports: ggplot2 (>= 3.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
